# AI-Investment-Assistant-Governed

A Python-based AI investment assistant built for Model Risk / Validation portfolios. Includes data fetching, indicators, signals, ML model, drift checks, explainability, audit logs, and a Streamlit UI.

## Quick Start (Local)

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install -e .
python scripts/run_demo.py --symbol AAPL
```

## Streamlit UI

```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

## Environment Keys (Optional)

```bash
export FRED_API_KEY="YOUR_FRED_KEY"
export NEWSAPI_KEY="YOUR_NEWSAPI_KEY"
```

